lead_paragraph: Karolina Pliskova kept alive her hopes for a berth at the WTA Finals with a win over Alexandra Dulgheru in the first round of the Kremlin Cup in Moscow. Carla Suárez Navarro beat Dominika Cibulkova.

headline.main: Two Bolster Hopes for Finals Berths
headline.print_headline: Two Bolster Hopes for Finals Berths
